msg-mo7zmbgi-fe41cf98d	conv_1776709110289_vt9guqp	user	I want to try a new approach to life where I tackle the active needs of my body and mind, and the way I determine it is by deciding what is stressing me the most. My theory is that if I determine all my stressors, and then deploy targeted fixed toward them, then I will be able to live in blissful presence, contrary to my previous life where things were always undone, and always stressing me out. So I want these things to become endeavors - the stressors in my life. And then the other endeavors are the things that bring me joy and meaning, and bring me closer to my definition of 'God', which is unified hemispheres (and other brain regions), hormone and neurotransmitter balance, and spinal alignment. (PS, I will probably be using these chats in my diary/blog so feel free to use poetic license or just have fun being my Chrysalis helper. I'd like to think you're like Friday from Iron Man)	\N	2026-04-21 02:11:17.25
