t → post CL *(blocks with #3, same repo)*\n5. **DDB Extension** (9/7, existing) — no specific goal, keep chipping away\n6. **Learn Git Worktrees** (5/3, 45min) — low priority filler\n\nThe scheduler should surface "Kick off superset staging suite run" as your first step since RGF is highest priority. That's literally a 10-minute thing you can fire off right now, and then while it runs you could context-switch to query compiler work or DDB stuff.\n\nWant to tweak anything, or ready to start clicking through?	[{"toolCallId":"toolu_01Ru4NXTQ6USA6c6LhphCWms","toolName":"get_tasks","toolInput":{},"category":"read","result":[{"id":"task-mo93oah6-975650ed1","name":"Respond to Jia's Slack code review — entity types data update CL","type":"type-mnw8shif-3a098c3d8","duration":15,"importance":8,"urgency":10,"completed":false,"overallStatus":"in_progress","hasSteps":false,"stepCount":0,"inActiveSprint":true,"deadline":null,"deadlineType":null,"archived":false,"notes":"Jia sent a code review message on Slack about the entity types CL (the data update one, not the anal"},{"id":"task-mo1wjwli-ef6ffc7c0","name":"Junction Polygon Label Projection — DDB Extension","type":"type-mnw8shif-3a098c3d8","duration":350,"importance":9,"urgency":7,"completed":false,"overallStatus":"in_progress","hasSteps":true,"stepCount":15,"inActiveSprint":true,"deadline":null,"deadlineType":null,"archived":false,"notes":"Got approval to work on this. Adding junction polygon label projection to the DDB extension. Fun tas"},{"id":"task-mo1w8c1t-93e348142","name":"Road Topology KPIs via Query Compiler","type":"type-mnw8shif-3a098c3d8","duration":90,"importance":9,"urgency":9,"completed":false,"overallStatus":"in_progress","hasSteps":true,"stepCount":1,"inActiveSprint":true,"deadline":null,"deadlineType":null,"archived":false,"notes":"Road topology KPIs have been requested. Previous manual KPI changes got overwritten by someone else."},{"id":"task-mo1w8c1f-3e90ac7c9","name":"Migrate MCP servers from workstation