summary-mnxhaxg4-0d89b2bd7	session_1776026596470_zisip0d	conv_1776097419866_j0jmhnq	The user provided updates on multiple concurrent workflows including test tagging research (mostly done but needs to review actual changes), adding an MCP tool to their cloud bot (added as a new step), setting up an index repository on their laptop, and completing dashboard work on the wait condition fusion task. The assistant helped track progress across these tasks, add workflow steps, and log missed time.	["Research test tagging step left as in_progress rather than complete since user still needs to review actual changes","MCP tool step added to the workflow before the research step","Created a new 'Set Up Index Repository on Laptop' workflow to enable multitasking across laptop and workstation","Dashboard work (~15 min) to be logged against the Wait Condition Fusion task","Next steps include forming agent memories and editing MCP configuration"]	[]	10	2026-04-13 17:40:51.028
summary-mnzacjgt-23ab142c1	session_1776209557292_hp17kz5	conv_1776209568791_avgpzo0	The user (app creator) started a brand new session to walk through the app step by step and note issues. They set up initial task type categories, brainstormed tasks related to leaving Glacier, Washington to drive back to Seattle the next morning, and began building out a schedule with a drive, massage, and sauna session.	["Created six task types: Personal Health, Work, Music, Social, Errands, and Chores","Errands and Chores are separate categories — errands are 'out of the house' tasks, chores are 'at home' tasks for easier context-based grouping","The drive from Glacier to Seattle should be a scheduled time block (not a task) at 8 AM tomorrow, approximately 2 hours","Pre-departure chores created: clean out fridge, take out trash, tidy up house, pack up laundry","Massage scheduled at 2 PM tomorrow for 2 hours, followed by sauna time"]	[]	11	2026-04-15 00:01:41.261
summary-mo7yjs9m-e2ed25bfc	session_1776709103518_hc4cf62	conv_1776709110289_vt9guqp	```json\n{\n  "summary": "The user began setting up their task planning system during a major life transition (leaving NVIDIA, 12-year relationship ending, exploring music/neuroscience). They established time tracking with five task types (Woody, NVIDIA, Health, Music, Cleanliness) and logged a full day of activities including chores, a 2-hour drive with singing, NVIDIA work at their mountain dome, grocery shopping, cooking, and two dog walks.",\n  "keyDecisions": [\n    "Created five task types for time tracking: Woody, NVIDIA, Health, Music, and Cleanliness",\n    "Committed to diligent time tracking as a core practice",\n    "Groceries and cooking categorized under Health; singing during drives categorized under Music",\n    "Cleanliness added as a separate category rather than folding chores into Health"\n  ],\n  "memoriesExtracted": [\n    {"category": "fact", "key": "dog_name", "value": "Has a dog named Woody"},\n    {"category": "fact", "key": "living_situation", "value": "Lives at/near a mountain dome location"},\n    {"category": "fact", "key": "life_transition", "value": "Leaving NVIDIA, ending 12-year relationship, exploring music and neuroscience — calls this period 'Mountain Chrysalis'"},\n    {"category": "fact", "key": "current_employer", "value": "Still working at NVIDIA (transitioning out)"},\n    {"category": "preference", "key": "time_tracking", "value": "Wants to track time diligently throughout the day"},\n    {"category": "pattern", "key": "singing_practice", "value": "Sings during long drives as music practice"},\n    {"category": "preference", "key": "logging_precision", "value": "Comfortable with best-guess time estimates rather than exact times"},\n    {"category": "fact", "key": "wake_time", "value": "Woke up around 7:30 AM"},\n    {"category": "pattern", "key": "dog_walks", "value": "Takes Woody on two ~20-minute walks during the workday"}\n  ]\n}\n```	[]	